    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/563145f64466d0b5de04c1f6cc8806ab.avif?t=1742008436\" width=386 height=386 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&quot;</strong>这次一定要交到女朋友，趁还来得及！<strong>&quot;</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里有一个30年从未有过女朋友的男人，太秀。如今，他面对着年纪渐长却没有任何恋爱前景的残酷现实。他意识到，如果没有路，那就得自己开辟一条。决心通过约会应用寻找新爱的单身狗，开始了他人生中可能是最大的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入我们，看看你的选择将如何改变他的命运！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[主要目标]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/124ada8f593aa8ee0d9061eaff59383a.poster.avif?t=1742008436\" width=360 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/124ada8f593aa8ee0d9061eaff59383a.webm?t=1742008436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/124ada8f593aa8ee0d9061eaff59383a.mp4?t=1742008436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单身狗心中有着脆弱的自尊，认为只要用心，就能找到任何女朋友。然而，当他自信地登录约会应用时，却遭遇了残酷的恋爱等级制度。他被分配到最低的青铜等级，极大地打击了他的自尊心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无法接受自己是青铜等级的事实，单身狗决心通过最终达到黄金等级来证明自己的恋爱能力，并在这个过程中找到真正的爱情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[你会做出怎样的选择？]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/8842f4b282f9980656538f6aff7e49aa.avif?t=1742008436\" width=688 height=386 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然单身狗在与人交谈方面有些挣扎，但他有一个秘密武器：恋爱建议装置“助智”！在“助智”的指导下，他希望能够应对任何尴尬的情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而…这个“助智”隐藏着一个惊人的秘密…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[游戏玩法]</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/4be58b64d49dd24e67408b1e1e6165a6.avif?t=1742008436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras_big/4be58b64d49dd24e67408b1e1e6165a6.avif?t=1742008436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1. 约会应用互动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您正在观察使用约会应用的单身狗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在约会应用中找到与单身狗有缘的她，并发送爱心给她！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果她对单身狗表现出兴趣，请接受匹配，视频通话将开始。<strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>2. 回答选择</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在与她的对话中，单身狗会面临如何回答的问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这时，请为单身狗选择合适的回答。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据您给出的回答，观察单身狗是否能获得她的好感，或是让她产生反感！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3. 在约会应用上升级</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前，单身狗被分配在最低的恋爱等级——青铜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与单身狗的缘分积累好感，获得恋爱积分，最终达到恋爱等级黄金！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在约会应用中遇到的她们可能对单身狗友好，也可能是敌对的。为了达到恋爱等级黄金，您需要采取战略性行动，只与命中注定的对象相遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果单身狗达到恋爱等级黄金，一位恋爱等级钻石的美丽女孩将等待着他！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>[游戏特点]</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/ebbd677b5e47dd168899765b72315df3.avif?t=1742008436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras_big/ebbd677b5e47dd168899765b72315df3.avif?t=1742008436 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仿佛在使用真实约会应用的沉浸感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验视频通话的真实感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各具魅力角色的故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让单身狗变成恋爱捕食者的成就感</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras/dc8d9a5d7021e52b91667f315e309133.avif?t=1742008436\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262250/extras_big/dc8d9a5d7021e52b91667f315e309133.avif?t=1742008436 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你会改变他那绝望的生活吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验一个真实的约会应用模拟，看看你的选择如何影响一切！</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《单身狗：在约会应用上升级》</strong></h2>",
